data.revised_prompt: An enticing and appetizing image showcasing a dish of Orange Chicken Stir Fry. The dish consists of crispy, golden chicken pieces tossed in a tangy orange sauce, sprinkled with sesame seeds, and accompanied by a variety of vibrant, sautéed vegetables like bell peppers and broccoli. The image captures the beauty of the dish with professional lighting that highlights its rich colors and textures. The setting is a rustic wooden table, with relevant accessories such as chopsticks and a small bowl of rice, all of which contributes to a professional food photography aesthetic.
